{
  "stem": "16245.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the next thing was that they pressed Jews into ghettos in all country towns, villages, country towns.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And within two months, there was not a single Jew left in the provinces outside of Budapest.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Within two months they managed to ship something like 6-- 800,000 Jews to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "At that time, there were close to a million Jews in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we still lived there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They never got around to it at that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They, as a first step, I imagine, they put Jews into Jewish houses, which meant that they designated houses as Jewish, Jewish apartment blocks or Jewish houses.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The house received a big yellow star on the outside.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the gate was kept locked all the time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all Jews had to move there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But oddly, Christians didn't have to move out of these houses.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Some remained.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That become a Jewish house, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That meant that we didn't have to move at all.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not at that time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, there was no guards, but there was a janitor who had to open and shut the door each time somebody came or went.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he wasn't really allowed to allow any, any Jew out at all, except in designated times, a couple of hours a day for shopping or something of that sort.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Judenhaus.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Look, obviously by then, we could see that the writing was on the wall.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And our elders still didn't want to see it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But young people were probably more with it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know how.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You see, what you have to remember is that you were brought up to be God-fearing and law-abiding citizens.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, you discover that the law is out to destroy you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And obviously, you have to readjust your thinking.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
